{"tid":653394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「奇警」再現觀塘警署！舉「貪腐」標語　控訴高層咁夠薑？","createTime":"2018-05-04T16:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T07:51:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":258,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"953053d46bfdc8fc83e1a58353dc09d6fdb662fb","tid":653394,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180505/large/1525449906_2574.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F1525449906_2574.png&h=8d7a6136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「奇警」再現觀塘警署！一名綽號「番薯」、駐守觀塘警署的軍裝高級警員，疑因與指揮官有過節，去年11月初手持「SORRY SIR」紙牌，在警署停車場跪地，成為城中熱話。事隔半年，「奇警」再在署內抗議，他昨午（4日）在停車場舉起寫上「貪腐」標語，吸引不少人目光和拍照，《蘋果》獨家收到有關照片。警方證實此事，表示一直適當跟進該同袍情況，並以關心及體諒的態度，向他提供適切支援。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科回覆《蘋果》查詢時指，一名駐守觀塘警區軍裝部、負責內勤支援工作的警務人員，昨日午膳時間於觀塘警署停車場展示字句，其後返回工作崗位，並確認他去年11月初，亦曾在觀塘警署停車場展示字句。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，該名高級警員綽號「番薯」，入職警隊約20年，先後在多個警區、機動部隊（PTU）及衝鋒隊工作，2013年被派駐將軍澳警區，駐守PTU期間，疑因超時津貼少收約700元，遂向上司投訴。據悉，有人查證後，發現派錢時可能出錯，遂私下給他錢，以平息風波，但事主性格偏執，拒絕收下這筆由上司自掏腰包的補償，堅持要投訴到底，至2014年7月，問題終獲解決。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，當時某長官曾向事主稱「件事解決咗，你係咪應該向阿sir講聲sorry先」，事主當時並沒有道歉，但懷疑因此事耿耿於懷，其後在警長升級試中失利，不滿情緒更深。事主其後被調到觀塘警署工作，而與他有過節的上司，去年8月又調到觀塘警區擔任指揮官，冤家相逢。事主其後多次在停車場，向指揮官辦公室默站抗議，其行為引起管理層關注，叫他不用「陀槍」，只負責做內勤支援工作。<br />\n<br />\n至去年11月初，事主趁午飯時間手持「SORRY SIR」紙牌，在停車場跪地，引起警署上下關注。有人更拍下放上網，照片在網上瘋傳，惹來很大爭議。警方當時指，一直適當跟進有關警務人員的福利事宜，並向其提供適切支援。"},{"pid":"3cba6a9c148c76ae95cef378fee65c7f85361ebc","tid":653394,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180505/58152758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58152758&d=FFGA5gNHdyuqgHvCYt6Uk8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2952950f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58152758&h=c631e5c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180505/58152758</a>"},{"pid":"90e3956c377ef6f3f25fd17ec725eea5c9a3c838","tid":653394,"uid":181819,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T16:31:47.000Z","msg":"豬扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f66b6375b8346ad29aa6ed25afd3099f96cbc61","tid":653394,"uid":41311,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:31:49.000Z","msg":"生菜 排骨"},{"pid":"79bd312509737b9708757d240a837a71dcf28cd8","tid":653394,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"極危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84a55607007738e8d4a098d40eaf78c9843a950","tid":653394,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b469113ac559235af640b63848ca66b8b7730abe","tid":653394,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2532c852d9d0054a7dd4315c69e6b8cbc6b9a5","tid":653394,"uid":189,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:51:26.000Z","msg":"傷心柴就求其啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4236a19e0b83a7b561dd987ab8a2ba909010fb46","tid":653394,"uid":92017,"like":272,"dislike":2,"score":270,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:54:17.000Z","msg":"跟返規矩程序做野叫性格偏執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走精面係醒目蠱惑，但唔駛污名化一d係錢銀問題上按規矩做野既人下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢上司私下比錢佢，根本收又死唔收又死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔收就自己蝕700；收左就可能以後比人當痛腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4eb17797e74543312e570be532b3c03fcea041b","tid":653394,"uid":1166,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:55:19.000Z","msg":"徐步高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853c52111c2b8b155735f695d48d335282c9feb8","tid":653394,"uid":28181,"like":199,"dislike":2,"score":197,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>，疑因超時津貼少收約700元，遂向上司投訴。據悉，有人查證後，發現派錢時可能出錯，遂私下給他錢，以平息風波，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但事主性格偏執</span></span></strong>，拒絕收下這筆由上司自掏腰包的補償，堅持要投訴到底</blockquote><br />\n乜L野性格偏執，程序出錯要查好撚正常，今次日700唔知派左去邊，下次700萬。"},{"pid":"ed2170afcddec5d1ed3ece466c7b21ccd264cf64","tid":653394,"uid":147242,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"陰公 槍都無得揸"},{"pid":"566bbc343417c6a222fe3e166a7ac986a6e604d7","tid":653394,"uid":157362,"like":185,"dislike":1,"score":184,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:06:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a60b198d3294d82ad04964ce27565f1ce7b4201","tid":653394,"uid":23592,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:12:20.000Z","msg":"番薯sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2098ade9932da14e4d0812a02af7040c46c2a370","tid":653394,"uid":13845,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"有性格,惦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻隻差佬都成隻狗咁款<br />\n應該要多啲呢種差佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9565e50c0091077a713f1ea844fcd8a35626c2ee","tid":653394,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:15:40.000Z","msg":"㾒左線<img src=\"/asse